2015-07-31  BABAROT  <b4b4r07@gmail.com>

	* v2.1.1

	* enhancd.sh: add a dot option
	  When enhancd takes a dot (`.`) string as an argument, it behaves like
	  a [zsh-bd](https://github.com/Tarrasch/zsh-bd) plugin. In short, you
	  can jump back to a specific directory, without doing `cd ../../...`.
	* README.md: add some documentations
